🛒 E-Commerce Sales Analysis (Excel)

Objective:
Analyze e-commerce sales data to understand customer behavior, sales performance, delivery efficiency, and product demand.

Key Work Done:
-Cleaned and structured raw transactional data
-Created calculated fields and KPIs (sales, quantity, ratings, delivery time)
-Built interactive PivotTables and PivotCharts
-Designed a fully interactive Excel dashboard with slicers
-Key Metrics & Analysis:
-Total Orders, Total Sales Amount, Quantity Sold
-Average Customer Rating
-Average Delivery Time
-Weekly sales and quantity trends
-Popular products analysis
-Order distribution by gender and order mode
-Delivery time distribution
